OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will be cloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, this heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes, the odd fog patch. The rain
OL,8,Fwill clear to sunny spells and showers
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon. Fresh to strong
OL,10,Fsoutherly winds across Shetland later
OL,11,Fthis morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening with
OL,14,Fsome late brightness. The rest of the
OL,15,Fnight will be mainly dry with variable
OL,16,Famounts of cloud and just the odd
OL,17,Fpassing shower.
OL,18,
OL,19,CSaturday:FA dry day with variable
OL,20,Famounts of cloud and some bright or
OL,21,Fsunny spells. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
